{
	"info": {
		"name": "Doctor Clinic API",
		"description": "Doctor Clinic API – Auth endpoints\n\n## Token Auto-Storage\n\nAll Login/Register responses include a **Tests** script that automatically stores `access_token`, `refresh_token`, and `expires_in` as collection variables. No manual copy-paste needed.\n\n## Authenticated Requests\n\nThe **Auth** folder has a **Pre-request Script** that attaches `Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}` to every request automatically.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "doctor-clinic"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:8000",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "access_token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "refresh_token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"description": "All authentication operations.\n\n**Pre-request Script** attaches the Bearer token automatically for protected routes.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register Patient",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', json.access_token);",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', json.refresh_token);",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('expires_in', json.expires_in);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"first_name\": \"Ahmed\",\n    \"last_name\": \"Ali\",\n    \"username\": \"ahmedali\",\n    \"email\": \"patient@example.com\",\n    \"phone\": \"+963912345678\",\n    \"address\": \"Damascus, Syria\",\n    \"gender\": \"male\",\n    \"birthday_date\": \"1995-06-15\",\n    \"password\": \"Password@123\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register/patient",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register", "patient"]
						}
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Created",
							"status": "Created",
							"code": 201,
							"body": "{\n    \"access_token\": \"eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1Qi...\",\n    \"refresh_token\": \"def50200...\",\n    \"expires_in\": 31536000,\n    \"token_type\": \"Bearer\",\n    \"user\": {\n        \"id\": \"019e1d0f-1ec6-7289-8cb3-eb9bdb0f1009\",\n        \"first_name\": \"Ahmed\",\n        \"last_name\": \"Ali\",\n        \"email\": \"patient@example.com\",\n        \"role\": \"patient\",\n        \"phone\": \"+963912345678\",\n        \"address\": \"Damascus, Syria\",\n        \"gender\": \"male\",\n        \"birthday_date\": \"1995-06-15\",\n        \"is_active\": true\n    }\n}"
						}
					]
				},
